name: WorkTimeTracker
0:
”Alexa, open Work Time Tracker”
”Alexa, ask Work Time Tracker to start a new timer”
”Alexa, tell Work Time Tracker I am about to start work”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: work time tracker
des:
Track how long you spend working by starting a timer when you start working and stopping it when you are finished.
You can see how long you have spent at any time by asking "how long have I been working?"
